{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":806,"text":"I would like to share with you today"},{"time":2306,"text":"a project that has changed how I approach"},{"time":4460,"text":"and practice architecture:"},{"time":6371,"text":"the Fez River Rehabilitation Project."}]},{"cues":[{"time":9299,"text":"My hometown of Fez, Morocco,"},{"time":11640,"text":"boasts one of the largest walled\nmedieval cities in the world,"},{"time":15307,"text":"called the medina, nestled in a river valley."},{"time":18046,"text":"The entire city is a UNESCO World Heritage Site."},{"time":21634,"text":"Since the 1950s, as the\npopulation of the medina grew,"},{"time":25610,"text":"basic urban infrastructure"},{"time":27530,"text":"such as green open spaces and sewage"},{"time":30460,"text":"quickly changed and got highly stressed."},{"time":35110,"text":"One of the biggest casualties of the situation"},{"time":38065,"text":"was the Fez River, which bisects\nthe medina in its middle"},{"time":42028,"text":"and has been considered for many centuries"},{"time":45000,"text":"as the city's very soul."},{"time":47572,"text":"In fact, one can witness the presence"},{"time":49990,"text":"of the river's extensive water network"},{"time":53170,"text":"all throughout the city,"},{"time":54451,"text":"in places such as private and public fountains."}]},{"cues":[{"time":58072,"text":"Unfortunately, because of the pollution of the river,"},{"time":61921,"text":"it has been covered little by little"},{"time":64357,"text":"by concrete slabs since 1952."},{"time":67431,"text":"This process of erasure was coupled"},{"time":70859,"text":"with the destruction of many houses"},{"time":72895,"text":"along the river banks"},{"time":74387,"text":"to be able to make machineries"},{"time":76376,"text":"enter the narrow pedestrian network of the medina."},{"time":81040,"text":"Those urban voids quickly became illegal parking"},{"time":84335,"text":"or trash yards."},{"time":86291,"text":"Actually, the state of the river"},{"time":88260,"text":"before entering the medina is pretty healthy."},{"time":91535,"text":"Then pollution takes its toll,"},{"time":93830,"text":"mainly due to untreated sewage"},{"time":96249,"text":"and chemical dumping from crafts such as tanning."},{"time":99900,"text":"At some point, I couldn't bear"},{"time":101950,"text":"the desecration of the river,"},{"time":103605,"text":"such an important part of my city,"},{"time":106335,"text":"and I decided to take action,"},{"time":107986,"text":"especially after I heard that the city"},{"time":110321,"text":"received a grant to divert sewage water"},{"time":113415,"text":"and to treat it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115035,"text":"With clean water, suddenly"},{"time":116992,"text":"the uncovering of the river became possible,"},{"time":119467,"text":"and with luck and actually a lot of pushing,"},{"time":122347,"text":"my partner Takako Tajima and I"},{"time":124563,"text":"were commissioned by the city to\nwork with a team of engineers"},{"time":128194,"text":"to uncover the river."},{"time":130302,"text":"However, we were sneaky,"},{"time":132257,"text":"and we proposed more:"},{"time":133574,"text":"to convert riverbanks into pedestrian pathways,"},{"time":138250,"text":"and then to connect these pathways"},{"time":140210,"text":"back to the city fabric,"},{"time":141853,"text":"and finally to convert the urban voids"},{"time":144406,"text":"along the riverbanks into public spaces"},{"time":147837,"text":"that are lacking in the Medina of Fez."},{"time":150187,"text":"I will show you briefly now"},{"time":151954,"text":"two of these public spaces."}]},{"cues":[{"time":154991,"text":"The first one is the Rcif Plaza,"},{"time":157771,"text":"which sits actually right on top of the river,"},{"time":160853,"text":"which you can see here in dotted lines."},{"time":163890,"text":"This plaza used to be a chaotic transportation hub"},{"time":167557,"text":"that actually compromised the urban integrity"},{"time":169481,"text":"of the medina, that has the largest"},{"time":171849,"text":"pedestrian network in the world."},{"time":174448,"text":"And right beyond the historic\nbridge that you can see here,"},{"time":177553,"text":"right next to the plaza,"},{"time":179364,"text":"you can see that the river looked like"},{"time":181524,"text":"a river of trash."},{"time":183785,"text":"Instead, what we proposed is to make"},{"time":186017,"text":"the plaza entirely pedestrian,"},{"time":188375,"text":"to cover it with recycled leather canopies,"},{"time":191278,"text":"and to connect it to the banks of the river."}]},{"cues":[{"time":195030,"text":"The second site of intervention"},{"time":196914,"text":"is also an urban void along the river banks,"},{"time":199920,"text":"and it used to be an illegal parking,"},{"time":202267,"text":"and we proposed to transform it"},{"time":203722,"text":"into the first playground in the medina."},{"time":206797,"text":"The playground is constructed using recycled tires"},{"time":210525,"text":"and also is coupled with a constructed wetland"},{"time":213360,"text":"that not only cleans the water of the river"},{"time":215790,"text":"but also retains it when floods occur."}]},{"cues":[{"time":219381,"text":"As the project progressed and\nreceived several design awards,"},{"time":222412,"text":"new stakeholders intervened"},{"time":224680,"text":"and changed the project goals and design."},{"time":228458,"text":"The only way for us to be able to bring"},{"time":231240,"text":"the main goals of the project ahead"},{"time":234532,"text":"was for us to do something very unusual"},{"time":236962,"text":"that usually architects don't do."},{"time":238874,"text":"It was for us to take our design ego"},{"time":242126,"text":"and our sense of authorship"},{"time":243602,"text":"and put it in the backseat"},{"time":245736,"text":"and to focus mainly on being activists"},{"time":248245,"text":"and on trying to coalesce"},{"time":250150,"text":"all of the agendas of stakeholders"},{"time":252441,"text":"and focus on the main goals of the project:"},{"time":255264,"text":"that is, to uncover the river, treat its water,"},{"time":257796,"text":"and provide public spaces for all."},{"time":259790,"text":"We were actually very lucky,"},{"time":261282,"text":"and many of those goals happened"},{"time":263825,"text":"or are in the process of happening."},{"time":265418,"text":"Like, you can see here in the Rcif Plaza."},{"time":267478,"text":"This is how it looked like about six years ago."},{"time":270169,"text":"This is how it looks like today."},{"time":272251,"text":"It's still under construction,"},{"time":273983,"text":"but actually it is heavily used"},{"time":275480,"text":"by the local population."},{"time":277123,"text":"And finally, this is how the Rcif Plaza will look like"},{"time":279946,"text":"when the project is completed."},{"time":281831,"text":"This is the river, covered, used as a trash yard."},{"time":285829,"text":"Then after many years of work,"},{"time":287651,"text":"the river with clean water, uncovered."},{"time":290385,"text":"And finally, you can see here the river"},{"time":292410,"text":"when the project will be completed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":294851,"text":"So for sure, the Fez River Rehabilitation"},{"time":297292,"text":"will keep on changing and adapting"},{"time":299710,"text":"to the sociopolitical landscape of the city,"},{"time":301938,"text":"but we strongly believe that by reimagining"},{"time":304998,"text":"the role and the agency of the architect,"},{"time":307439,"text":"we have set up the core idea\nof the project into motion;"},{"time":311398,"text":"that is, to transform the river from sewage"},{"time":313907,"text":"to public space for all,"},{"time":315561,"text":"thereby making sure that the city of Fez"},{"time":318733,"text":"will remain a living city for its inhabitants"},{"time":320960,"text":"rather than a mummified heritage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":323120,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":324856,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}